  "texts": [
    "to reconstruct the original inputs using the crucial feature.",
    "Autoencoders reduce the data dimension by keeping the features required to reconstruct the data.",
    "The output of the autoencoders is considered the same as inputs, but with some loss.",
    "Thus, sometimes, it is called lossy compression.",
    "Considering X as a data sample n is the number of samples and m number of features and Y the encoder output (the reduced dimension of X)."
  ]
}